dct_description_sm: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows cadastral, district, municipal, property, kiburga or county block, final certificate boundaries; main power line, and tree plantations. "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "Air photography by Fairey Air Survey Ltd.; field survey data by the Department of Lands and Surveys." Includes index to sheets. "300-6-66." ©Copyright Uganda Government 1966.
